osad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解一個平民會覺得比一個國家嘅元首、機關知得更多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國要出手唔會關你和平定暴力事，係講利益。"},{"pid":"8bd341955e95b622e25b7cc024a83b4298caa0fa","tid":1238961,"uid":148987,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T04:30:30.000Z","msg":"出面成班分化撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5da40f8f2d413f7bcdfabdb5ae931f853641a865","tid":1238961,"uid":62247,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"754e500af724dec3c5cab65c951b05ad1ce8dc83","tid":1238961,"uid":66260,"like":140,"dislike":3,"score":137,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T04:11:07.000Z","msg":"人地陳浩天幾年前開始去外國見使節, 演講<br />\n上年FCC單野幾乎全世界都識佢<br />\n咁搵個有知名度既人去係咪用得多呀? 起碼多啲人聽你up呀<br />\n佢唔去G20唔通搵陳云根條廢老去大鵬展翅呀?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T04:32:55.000Z","msg":"大鵬展翅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cbdd253885076893f503369f42a1c6a2d166cea","tid":1238961,"uid":262557,"like":4,"dislike":11,"score":-7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T04:33:18.000Z","msg":"佢係受熱比亞果的彊獨藏獨組織要請去<br />\n唔係好信唔講港獨囉<br />\n佢依家咁群埋班人<br />\n唔講都當你係<br />\n知唔知咩叫避忌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43e3cdc4d58f61de8ddf8b697e979a025fd1c18b","tid":1238961,"uid":66260,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"3cbdd253885076893f503369f42a1c6a2d166cea","tid":1238961,"uid":262557,"like":4,"dislike":11,"score":-7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T04:33:18.000Z","msg":"佢係受熱比亞果的彊獨藏獨組織要請去<br />\n唔係好信唔講港獨囉<br />\n佢依家咁群埋班人<br />\n唔講都當你係<br />\n知唔知咩叫避忌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T04:53:19.000Z","msg":"因為佢群埋班人係獨派, 佢以前又講開獨<br />\n所以佢今次一定係提港獨<br />\n師兄正職做緊選舉主任?"},{"pid":"476c313aa3a575d1760597e73777fa580df4f159","tid":1238961,"uid":8511,"lik